<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">د ع ر:</span> <span class="c2">(الدَّعَرُ)</span> بِفَتْحَتَيْنِ وَ <span class="c2">(الدَّعَارَةُ)</span> بِالْفَتْحِ الْخُبْثُ وَالْفِسْقُ وَبَابُهُ طَرِبَ وَسَلِمَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(دَاعِرٌ)</span> وَهِيَ <span class="c2">(دَاعِرَةٌ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>